A%2F%2Fwww.spca.org.hk%2Fch%2Fservices%2Fhoming-animals&d=DXuv2gayA%2Byyjyt3RGK41M3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=f38bacac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.spca.org.hk/ch/services/homing-animals</a> 樓主可以考慮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T11:32:19.000Z","msg":"thanks<br />\n晏啲睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T12:52:28.000Z","msg":"通常放得係愛協個d狗仔貓仔一定係好乖無嚴重病痛<br />\n因為愛協會幫佢地body check, 唔合格就會安樂死<br />\n有丁屎咁多既攻擊性都會安樂死<br />\n<br />\n而且愛協領養多數你做足佢地要求都會好快俾個動物你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓主考慮下領養啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88c7030d0182fb4d5c9ae9d8591dca8eb5e26435","tid":1492924,"uid":48738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T13:02:43.000Z","msg":"跪求樓主去領養狗狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好助長黑心繁殖場賺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bad344dfeb9b73ea72607148504cf679b28994b6","tid":1492924,"uid":266348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T13:27:27.000Z","msg":"支持領養，唔一定名犬先可愛，唐狗都一樣咁得意"}]}